<i>Go across the tracks</i> â™ª

1249
01:02:01.748 --> 01:02:06.132
â™ª <i>Where the viaduct looms</i>
<i>Like a bird of doom</i> â™ª

1250
01:02:06.259 --> 01:02:07.348
â™ª <i>As it shifts...</i> â™ª

1251
01:02:07.475 --> 01:02:09.877
[owner] Okay.
Get home safe. Bye. guys.

1252
01:02:10.003 --> 01:02:14.100
â™ª <i>Where secrets lie</i>
<i>In the border fires</i> â™ª

1253
01:02:14.228 --> 01:02:16.020
â™ª <i>In the humming wires</i> â™ª

1254
01:02:16.148 --> 01:02:18.995
â™ª <i>Hey man. you know</i>
<i>You're never coming back</i> â™ª

1255
01:02:19.124 --> 01:02:21.044
â™ª <i>Past this square</i>
<i>Past the bridge</i> â™ª

1256
